item.description: 1.62.0 (Unreleased) Stabilize derive_default_enum Replace Linux Mutex and Condvar with futex based ones. Improve method name suggestions make unaligned_references lint deny-by-default and make it show up in future-breakage report Stabilize total_cmp Promote x86_64-unknown-none target to Tier 2 and distribute build artifacts Enforce Copy bounds for repeat elements while considering lifetimes linker: Stop using whole-archive on dependencies of dylibs Include nonexported macro_rules! macros in the doctest target
